    {
      "_id": "card_emmie_monitor",
      "title": "📊 Emmie Performance Monitor - Weekly Check",
      "description": "## Purpose\nTrack Emmie's inbox cleanup performance metrics and ensure consistent operation.\n\n## Metrics to Monitor\n- **Emails processed per run** (target: 150+)\n- **False positive rate** (should be <2%)\n- **Processing time** (target: <30 seconds)\n- **Uptime** (should be 99.9%+)\n- **Whitelist effectiveness** (no important emails deleted)\n- **Auto-file accuracy** (correct labels applied)\n\n## Weekly Check\n- **When:** Every Sunday evening\n- **Action:** Review Emmie's logs and metrics from the past week\n- **Location:** `/Users/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/agents/emmie/metrics.csv`\n- **Success:** All metrics within targets\n\n## Current Performance (Feb 20-24)\n- ✅ Runs consistently at 4 AM\n- ✅ 202 emails processed in latest run\n- ✅ ~100 deleted (promotional/newsletters)\n- ✅ ~100 filed (organized into labels)\n- ✅ No false positives reported\n- ✅ Whitelist working perfectly\n\n## Action Items\n- [ ] Review metrics every Sunday\n- [ ] Check for any false positives\n- [ ] Update whitelist if new important senders appear\n- [ ] Adjust rules if needed\n- [ ] Document any issues",
      "labels": [
        "Emmie",
        "Monitoring",
        "Weekly",
        "Performance"
      ],
      "priority": "Med",
      "column": "done",
      "order": 6,
      "createdAt": 1739991600000,
      "updatedAt": 1773351517341,
      "completedAt": 1773278776611
