      "title": "[Passive Income] Spreadsheet Template Store (Google Sheets/Excel)",
      "description": "1. Research top-selling spreadsheet templates on Etsy (categories, prices, reviews)\n2. Create 15-20 templates in Google Sheets:\n   - Small business: P&L tracker, invoice generator, inventory manager\n   - Personal finance: budget planner, debt payoff calculator, investment tracker\n   - Freelancer: project tracker, time logger, client CRM, invoice template\n   - Real estate: rental property calculator, mortgage comparison, ROI analyzer\n   - Restaurant: food cost calculator, menu pricing, staff schedule\n3. Each template must have:\n   - Professional formatting with conditional formatting and data validation\n   - Instructions tab with setup guide\n   - Sample data pre-filled\n   - Works in both Google Sheets and Excel\n4. Create Etsy store with optimized listings (SEO titles, tags, descriptions)\n5. Build Mission Control dashboard at /app/spreadsheet-store:\n   - Sales per template, total revenue\n   - Best sellers ranking\n   - Customer reviews/feedback\n   - Ideas queue for new templates\n6. Price at $5-12 each, bundles at $25-39\n\n---\nCONTEXT\n- Startup budget: $0\n- Manual steps (user must do): Upload to Etsy/Gumroad, create preview images, respond to customer questions\n- Source idea: idea_1709856009_tmpl01\n\n---\n**Task Executor Failed** (2026-03-08 05:04, exit: 1)\nTask timed out after 2 hours",
