      "title": "Research quality backlinks service: build an agent for ourselves + pay-per-use model",
      "description": "Deep research on creating high-quality backlinks. Explore:\n1. Backlink strategy & best practices (SEO, authority, relevance)\n2. Tools & automation for backlink generation\n3. Service model: use agent for own backlinks + offer as paid service to others\n4. Feasibility of agent building backlinks at scale\n5. Monetization: potential pricing, margins, customer acquisition\n6. Risk assessment: staying within Google guidelines, link quality\n7. Proof of concept: test on Joes own sites first\n\nGoal: Determine if this can be a standalone passive income service or integrated into existing offerings.\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-08 12:16)\nI'll tackle this in parallel — researching backlinks while exploring the existing codebase structure.",
