      "_id": "card_1773247988417",
      "title": "[Passive Income] AI Kids' Bedtime Story Personalization Engine",
      "description": "Build and deploy: Automated service creating personalized bedtime stories incorporating child's name, interests, and current challenges (moving, new sibling, etc.) with moral lessons and familiar characters.\n\n---\nCONTEXT\n- Startup budget: 45\n- Manual steps (user must do): Create story templates, moderate content for appropriateness, handle customer requests\n- Source idea: idea_1773182900348_5\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-12 04:32)\nThe background MC build also completed successfully. The task is done — everything I described above is live and working.",
