    {
      "title": "SEO Monitoring & Optimization for Mastermind HQ",
      "description": "Set up consistent SEO tracking and daily improvements for mastermindshq.business.\n\n## Objectives\n1. **Monitor & Track SEO** — Build a system to consistently pull and track Google Search Console data (impressions, clicks, CTR, position) for sc-domain:mastermindshq.business. GSC link: https://search.google.com/search-console/performance/search-analytics?resource_id=sc-domain:mastermindshq.business\n2. **Daily SEO Improvements** — Establish a daily routine/agent that identifies and implements SEO improvements (meta tags, content optimization, internal linking, keyword targeting).\n3. **Indexing & Agent-Friendliness** — Ensure all pages are indexed, robots.txt and sitemap.xml are optimal, and the site is friendly to AI agents and crawlers (structured data, semantic HTML, llms.txt).\nWe need to track this in a MastermindsHQ Missin Control Page too. Make sure to pull info for Google search console that is relevent. Make Chart. \n\n## Key Resources\n- Google Search Console: sc-domain:mastermindshq.business\n- Website: https://www.mastermindshq.business/ (Wix-hosted)\n- Related project: ~/.openclaw/workspace/projects/mastermind/\n\n---\n**Auto-executed by Task Executor** (2026-03-12 12:19)\nThe linter changes look fine — they're consistent with what I wrote. Everything is in place. The task is complete.",
